I can solve Sudoku puzzles. You can interact with me either by texting or by calling me on the phone.

You have to provide me with the puzzle you want to solve. On the phone you can speak the matrix, giving me numbers and 'blank' or 'space' for the empty cells. Or you can use your phone keypad, using '0' for an empty cell.

Once I have a solution, you can ask for the answer, but only by text. Or you can ask for a hint, specifying a row, column, or row and column together.
